quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  41,19,ﾃ疎lnde non ayﾉ兎 Allah ﾉ兎n mooﾉ妬roytee faade ka Yiite... Hara hiﾉ兎 ﾃｱoﾆｴﾆｴindiree
  41,20,"Haa si ﾉ兎 hewtii nge, nannﾉ容 maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ容n, e giiﾉ容 maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ容n, e guri ﾉ殿lli maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ擁n seeditoo e dow maﾉ橡兎, kon ko ﾉ兎 gollaynoo"
  41,21,"ﾆ‘ wi'ana guri maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ容n: \"Ko fii honnﾉ蓉m seeditaniﾉ熔n e amen?\" ﾆ各 wi'a: \"Ko Allah wowlinﾉ熔 kala huunde On, wowlini men. Ko Kanko tagunoo on gila ka laawol aranol, ko ka Makko kadi rutteteﾉ熔n"
  41,22,"On wonaali hiﾉ熔n suuﾉ熔ra, fii wata nanﾉ容 mon, e giiﾉ容 mon, e guri mon seedito e mon. Kono on sikkuno, wonnde Allah anndaa ko ﾉ蓉uﾉ擁 e ko huuwoton"
  41,23,"Ko ﾉ蓉m mooﾉ熔n, wonunoo ko sikkunoﾉ熔n Joomi mon, ﾉ蓉m halki on. Waﾉ葉inﾉ熔n jeyaaﾉ兎 e pertuﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n"
  41,24,"Hay si ﾉ兎 muﾃｱﾃｱike, ko Yiite ngen wonata jaaﾆｴorde maﾉ橡兎; si ﾉ兎 ﾉ預ﾉ橡妬i feleede accitee, ﾉ兎 wonaali feleteeﾉ兎 accitee"
  41,25,"Men wurtani ﾉ兎 wondiiﾉ兎, ﾉ兎n cuﾉ擁nani ﾉ兎 ko woni yeeso maﾉ橡兎, e ko woni ﾉ殿awo maﾉ橡兎. Konngol [lepte] ngol jojji e maﾉ橡兎, wondude e mofte yawtunooﾉ容 ado maﾉ橡兎, immorde e jinna e yimﾉ兎. Pellet, ﾉ兎 laatino hayruﾉ兎"